            <title>[Editor]Sublime Text 3 – 設置中文&amp;默認語法</title>
            <link>http://localhost:1313/2021/03/30/sublime-text-3-%E8%A8%AD%E7%BD%AE%E9%BB%98%E8%AA%8D%E8%AA%9E%E6%B3%95/</link>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Mar 2021 03:57:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <guid>http://localhost:1313/2021/03/30/sublime-text-3-%E8%A8%AD%E7%BD%AE%E9%BB%98%E8%AA%8D%E8%AA%9E%E6%B3%95/</guid>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;安裝:&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://www.sublimetext.com/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;官方網站&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;中文化:&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/102376540&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;參考網站&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;設置中文&#34;&gt;設置中文&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ctrl+Shift+P輸入:install package&lt;figure class=&#34;wp-block-image size-full&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;764&#34; height=&#34;164&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image-1.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-495&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image-1.png 764w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image-1-300x64.png 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 764px) 100vw, 764px&#34; /&gt; &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;再輸入Chinses，安裝完後重新開啟Sublime即可。&lt;figure class=&#34;wp-block-image size-full&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;995&#34; height=&#34;344&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-494&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image.png 995w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image-300x104.png 300w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image-768x266.png 768w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px&#34; /&gt; &lt;/figure&gt; &lt;figure class=&#34;wp-block-image size-large&#34;&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;393&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image-2-1024x393.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-496&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image-2-1024x393.png 1024w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image-2-300x115.png 300w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image-2-768x295.png 768w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2021/08/image-2.png 1084w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;設置默認語法&#34;&gt;設置默認語法&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;在Sublime Text 3中設置默認語法顯示，未來若再開啟文件的話會以該格式的語法顯示。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;View(檢視) -&amp;gt; Syntax(語法) -&amp;gt; Open all with current extension as … -&amp;gt; 選擇自己要的語法。&lt;figure class=&#34;wp-block-image&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img decoding=&#34;async&#34; src=&#34;https://i.imgur.com/meLD8TJ.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt; &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</description>
